o the finish line and festival. Over the 13.1 miles you will see beautiful =
mountain peaks, the Ventura River Basin, the Historic Ventura Downtown dist=
rict, and the world renowned Ventura Coast line. The finish line and festiv=
al are directly adjacent to the beach which beckons you for a post-race soa=
k. This USATF certified route (CA23034TEB) runs lightning fast!<br />
<br />
<br />
***Courses are subject to change without notice.<br />
<br />

