	<div class=3D"eventExtendedDetails">
		New to 2025, we are offering a multi event challenge! You will run the 5k=
 with us on Saturday and then the 10k on Sunday. <br />
<br />
As a Combo Challenge runner, you will get a special medal (three medals in =
total- 1 for the 5k, 1 for the 10k and 1 combo medal) and VIP lounge access=
 on Sun! <br />
<br />
The 5k is all beach front running on Saturday. Come ready to run <br />
 then hang out at the expo festival as the majority of the runners are chec=
king in that day for their race the next day.<br />
<br />
Then on Sunday join us for the Mountains 2 Beach 10k. Starting at roughly m=
ile 20 of the full marathon, the 10k runners get a taste of the same route =
as the full and half marathoners. Be sure to stick around for the festiviti=
es and beer garden and to cheer on your fellow runners. 10k participants wi=
ll enjoy the same finish line as the Marathoners and Half Marathoners, alon=
g with all the amenities and of course the Beachside Party afterwards. <br =
/>
